                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12519509" author="billa" created="Mon, 13 Aug 2007 20:08:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am going to update the JSP to behave the same way as Solr does in determining solr home:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) JNDI lookup&lt;br/&gt;
2) system property solr.solr.home&lt;br/&gt;
3) default to cwd&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ken, so you will need to do either 1) or 2) to set Solr home.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12519791" author="billa" created="Tue, 14 Aug 2007 21:51:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It turns out to be a very simple change in the JSP as it already has obtained solr home from solr.core.Config.  Attached in the patch.  I will apply it tomorrow if no one objects.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
